{"type": "article", "id": 31647, "title": "不靠工具和螺丝也能拼出一张书桌｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-08-30T23:06:37Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 32192, "name": "Kristina Dam Studio"}, {"id": 32193, "name": "UPSOP"}, {"id": 32194, "name": "Hochu rayu"}, {"id": 32195, "name": "dwiss"}, {"id": 32196, "name": "Tealicious"}, {"id": 32197, "name": "Lefteris Tsampikakis"}, {"id": 32198, "name": "Alvarez Juana"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 186, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160830232030GaYvcqV20KEzCxXZ.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Magnetosphere Desk Lamp by Lefteris Tsampikakis</h3><p>以自然界中两大基本力电磁力和引力为设计灵感，希腊设计师 <a href=\"http://www.lefteristsampikakis.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lefteris Tsampikakis</a> 打造了一款依靠磁性随意改变造型的台灯 <a href=\"http://www.lefteristsampikakis.com/#!magnetosphere-desk-lamp/whfg6\" rel=\"nofollow\">Magnetosphere</a>。金属灯柱底端的原木组件和白色的底座都具有磁性，你可以通过磁力让灯柱在球状的底座上自由移动位置。加上灯柱本身还能够旋转改变光的朝向，台灯因此能呈现出各种宛如天文仪器的造型。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608302323276jxG9vyQzFUD3c8b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.701667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160830232327VgxT9OZXD8A2riFY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.860833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160830232326JPwmWygEcv7B5nQu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.795833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160830232327h7aCvQWsoJgMOq5c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.795833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160830232327lGNDBz06JE9n4jA7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.795833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160830232327q2lkSWw04FcQJKXm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.697500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Book Keeper by Kristina Dam Studio</h3><p>如果你钟情于北欧的极简风格，丹麦 <a href=\"http://kristinadam.dk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kristina Dam Studio</a> 即将在巴黎时尚家居设计展秋展上展示的 Sculptural Minimalism 系列会在功能和视觉上同时满足你的需要。系列中这款名为 Book Keeper 的书架由两个锻接在一起的金属框架构成，处在上方的框架与底部形成了一个 45 度角的倾斜，使书籍的呈现方式更具装饰效果。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160830232345qzZAwrGIO3v1fQWL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713867\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160830232345cA4ILZx1fbCVmOt7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714844\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160830232345F29jV0rqfWdOJo3g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713867\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Butterply Desk by UPSOP</h3><p>来自香港的 <a href=\"http://www.upsop.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">UPSOP</a> 工作室最近设计了一张名为 <a href=\"http://butterply.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Butterply</a> 的工作桌，人们不需要依靠工具甚至螺丝就能徒手在一分钟内完成组装。为了满足人们对桌面高低的不同要求，Butterply 的桌腿还采用了一种特殊的延伸设计，可以在四种高度间进行调整，就算是不平的地面，只要回转桌腿也能进行微调。桌子还附带了四种桌面配件，能够让你一次性搞定电子产品、电线、书籍以及小物的收纳，让桌面显得整洁而且统一。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1038381675/butterply-desk-the-most-affordable-designer-furnit\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，根据桌子的大小和颜色售价从 79 到 450 美元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160830232246XiJqA4CQGue0zh1M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016083023224897e5sFWOYSpgd6wi.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714706\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160830232246zoPQ76ACLlBswhtN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160830232246F4EcKmvdHbo3p5Ck.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160830232246TlCq2yYkxUurthco.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.004451\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>VIGVAM hanger by Hochu rayu</h3><p>这款名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/36631473/Vigvam-hanger\" rel=\"nofollow\">VIGVAM</a> 的衣架是乌克兰 <a href=\"http://hochurayu.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hochu rayu</a> 设计工作室的作品，四根修长纤细的桦木棍构成了它的支架，你或许会把它认作一个未完成的篝火架或者是土著民的窝棚。由于组件的重量很轻而且还有一个配套的纸筒包装，无论是搬运还是组装起来都非常方便。极简的外形加上五颜六色的鹿角形挂钩使整个衣架带给人一种随性而活泼的感觉，也难怪工作室会以猎鹿为主题为它拍摄宣传照了。除此之外，你还能在包装上找到一头叉着腰的鹿。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608302322130TmkJYXiLeq6KrZF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.683333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160830232214DRlI2XGBPr9FiL5t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.965000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160830232214QmzN72XOISjteHaR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160830232211SyQjvUcVGXkRCgFq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160830232215LZaRxk6DCNgfl2Po.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160830232216z4NHwl0GKSQ6C3Ls.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>dwiss by dwiss</h3><p>有意识对垃圾进行分类却苦于没有合适的家用回收站？英国工作室 <a href=\"http://www.dwiss.org/\" rel=\"nofollow\">dwiss</a> 在设计咨询公司 <a href=\"http://www.designfutures-group.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Futures</a> 以及德国设计师 <a href=\"http://www.paultimmer.nl/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Paul Timmer</a> 的协助下打造了一款拥有四个隔间的同名回收站。dwiss 由上下两层构成，底层要比上层略高一些，而且被设计成了两个抽屉。抽屉和上层内置的回收桶一样，随时可以单独拆卸出来，使用起来更加灵活。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.dwiss.org/#!product-page/kddnq\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 895 英镑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160830232129MVyLXIWzbkAwqCni.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160830232130BNOYSiwDV4y5Ao1k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160830232129R9eF5JsrpXUo1QYi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160830232129ewgMqkdI1sK0xAba.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160830232129qIrjaGJOkxSMbvdz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Tealicious by Alvarez Juana</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.tealicious.it/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tealicious</a> 是一间由阿根廷茶迷 Marcela V.Esteban 在意大利佛罗伦萨创立的茶叶店，它的品牌设计委托了同样来自阿根廷的设计师 <a href=\"http://www.alvarezjuana.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alvarez Juana</a> 共同完成。考虑到所销售的茶叶品种时常发生变化，她们设计了一套清新而且直观的标示体系，让 Marcela 在销售时可以直接在标签上写下茶叶名，再圈选出它的构成、冲泡水温以及所需时间。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160830232102Cc30K6NYDdJMhRn2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.680208\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160830232103r2nKJqh3xd1SQ0UI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.184375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160830232102j0vOc3wdsLN7i2Go.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.680208\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160830232102mSMksGDHEhZi01Oq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160830232103manrR7NdqSsXlL0K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.679688\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160830232103iyELSFvfklKM4A9h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.680208\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}